The paper discusses the use of plug-and-play algorithms for MRI image recovery, which involves solving an inverse problem. This suggests that the paper could belong to the computer vision (cs.CV) or information theory (cs.IT) sub-categories. Additionally, the paper discusses the use of denoising subroutines, which is a common technique in machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also mentions the need for efficient reconstruction methods, which could fall under multimedia (cs.MM) or signal processing (cs.SI).
